msgstr ":guilabel:`创建驾驶员` 和 :guilabel:`创建未来驾驶员`的 :guilabel:`创建驾驶员` 形式完全相同。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:104
msgid ""
"Depending on the installed applications, different tabs or fields may be "
