msgstr ":guilabel:`公司名称...`：使用下拉菜单，选择驾驶员所属的公司。"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:121
#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:147
